	"Volume Sampler": "体积采样器",
	"Add a new constant stream to the input set\nIf the input is not given a single entry with the constant value is created.": "向输入集添加一个新的常量流。\n如果没有提供输入，则会创建一个包含该常量值的单条目数据。",
	"Adds one or more tags to FlowData.": "向 FlowData 添加一个或多个标签。",
	"Applies point attributes and optional transforms onto existing scene nodes.": "将点属性以及可选变换应用到现有场景节点。",
	"Generates a list of assets.\nUseful in combination with the Match And Set node, this node generates a list of meshes with some attribute/tag and weight assigned.": "生成一个资源列表。\n通常配合“匹配并设置”节点使用，用于生成带有属性/标签和权重的网格列表。",
	"Splits points by whether an attribute value falls inside a numeric range.\nEnable 'String Match Mode' to filter by comma-separated string values instead.": "根据属性值是否落在数值范围内拆分点。\n启用“字符串匹配模式”后，可改为按逗号分隔的字符串值过滤。",
	"Sets an attribute on points to random values or sequential indices.": "将点上的某个属性设置为随机值或顺序索引。",
	"Renames one attribute/stream while preserving its type and values.": "重命名一个属性/流，并保留其类型和值。",
	"Converts attribute rows into point data by providing position/rotation/size streams.": "通过提供位置、旋转和尺寸流，将属性行转换为点数据。",
	"Applies boolean logic between streams and writes the result as a bool stream.": "在流之间应用布尔逻辑，并将结果写为布尔流。",
	"Modifies the size/bounds property on points in the provided point data.": "修改给定点数据中点的尺寸/边界属性。",
	"Selects one of two outputs based on a Boolean attribute or value.": "根据布尔属性或值选择两个输出之一。",
	"Computes rotation from an up vector stream or constant and applies it to the points.": "根据上方向向量流或常量计算旋转，并应用到点上。",
	"UE naming alias for clipping point sets by Path3D polygons.": "用于按 Path3D 多边形裁剪点集的 UE 命名别名。",
	"Filters points against one or more Path3D or point-list polygons.": "根据一个或多个 Path3D 或点列表多边形过滤点。",
	"For each input Point Data, outputs a new Point Data containing a single point that encompasses all points in its respective Point Data.": "对每个输入点数据，输出一个只包含单点的新点数据，该点包围对应点数据中的全部点。",
	"Composes a Vector3 attribute from float attributes or default values.": "由浮点属性或默认值组合出 Vector3 属性。",
	"Copies points using linear repeat offsets or source-to-target placement mode.": "使用线性重复偏移或源到目标放置模式复制点。",
	"Godot-facing alias of Copy for point data.": "面向 Godot 点数据的“复制”别名。",
	"Godot-facing alias of Merge for point data.": "面向 Godot 点数据的“合并”别名。",
	"Generates a spline from all the input points.": "根据所有输入点生成一条样条。",
	"Creates bounds-style surface points from ordered polygon point streams.": "根据有序多边形点流创建边界式表面点。",
	"Creates one bounds-style surface point from each Path3D polygon/spline.": "从每个 Path3D 多边形/样条创建一个边界式表面点。",
	"Remaps the density of each point in the point data to another density value according to the provided curve.": "根据提供的曲线，将点数据中每个点的密度重映射为另一个密度值。",
	"Extracts one or more table rows into an attribute-set stream.": "将一个或多个表格行提取为属性集流。",
	"Reads data from a named graph variable declared by a Set Variable node.": "读取由设置变量节点声明的命名图变量数据。",
	"Forces the visualization of the debug node. Used when some specific values are required in the debug options.": "强制显示调试节点。用于调试选项需要特定值的情况。",
	"Decomposes a Vector3 attribute into three float attributes.": "将 Vector3 属性分解为三个浮点属性。",
	"Removes one or more tags from FlowData.": "从 FlowData 移除一个或多个标签。",
	"Applies a linear transform to the point densities.": "对点密度应用线性变换。",
	"Performs set operations between two point sets based on position/size overlap.": "根据位置/尺寸重叠关系，对两个点集执行集合操作。",
	"Creates a new attribute where the value is\nthe minimum distance from each point to any of the points in the second set.\nThe value can be normalized to an optional Max Distance": "创建一个新属性，其值为每个点到第二个点集中任意点的最小距离。\n该值可以按可选的最大距离归一化。",
	"Sets the point density according to the distance of each point from a reference point.": "根据每个点到参考点的距离设置点密度。",
	"Generates sequential L-shaped corridor floor points between selected rooms.": "在所选房间之间生成连续的 L 形走廊地面点。",
	"Expands single room center points into grid floor tiles covering their width and height.": "将单个房间中心点扩展为覆盖其宽度和高度的网格地面格点。",
	"Generates procedural floor, wall, pillar, and torch layout points using a grid room-carving algorithm.": "使用网格房间雕刻算法生成程序化地面、墙体、柱子和火把布局点。",
	"Generates a random set of room candidates snapped to grid, with priority, ID, and bounds.": "生成一组吸附到网格的随机房间候选，包含优先级、ID 和边界。",
	"Analyzes the FloorPoints set to output walls, doors, torches, and pillars.": "分析 FloorPoints 集合并输出墙体、门、火把和柱子。",
	"For each point, duplicate the point and move it along an axis defined by the Direction/Offset, and apply a transform on the new point.": "对每个点进行复制，沿 Direction/Offset 定义的轴移动，并对新点应用变换。",
	"Evaluates an expression and stores the result in the output stream\n * When expose_arrays is set, the values of the point set are exposed as arrays\n   and position[Index] (Index with capital I) must be used to reference the current point\n   and position[Index-1] references the previous position\n * Size for the total number of points\n * Customize the Node Label if the expression is too long": "计算表达式并将结果存入输出流。\n * 启用 expose_arrays 时，点集值会以数组形式暴露。\n   必须使用 position[Index]（Index 首字母大写）引用当前点。\n   position[Index-1] 引用前一个位置。\n * Size 表示点总数。\n * 如果表达式过长，可自定义节点标签。",
	"Filter inputs based on some condition.\nThis node returns splits the input stream in two substreams.": "根据条件过滤输入。\n该节点会将输入流拆分为两个子流。",
	"Separates data based on whether they have a specified metadata attribute.": "根据数据是否拥有指定元数据属性进行分离。",
	"Separates data according to their tags. You can specify a comma-separated list of Tags to filter by.": "根据标签分离数据。可以指定逗号分隔的标签列表作为过滤条件。",
	"Separates data based on their type, as dictated by the Target Type.": "根据目标类型指定的数据类型分离数据。",
	"Returns the number of entries in the input data.": "返回输入数据中的条目数量。",
	"Writes a sequential loop/index attribute for each incoming point.": "为每个输入点写入顺序循环/索引属性。",
	"UE naming alias of Size. Outputs total points as a single integer stream.": "Size 的 UE 命名别名。将点总数作为单个整型流输出。",
	"Generates a set of points in a grid spatial distribution,\nwhere the separation is step": "按网格空间分布生成一组点，\n点间距由 step 决定。",
	"Extracts exposed edge and corner points from filled grid cells.": "从已填充网格单元中提取外露边和角点。",
	"Connects ordered points with orthogonal grid-cell paths on the XZ plane.": "在 XZ 平面上，用正交网格单元路径连接有序点。",
	"Creates one point per grid cell inside input bounds, or inside configured bounds when no input is connected.": "在输入边界内为每个网格单元创建一个点；没有连接输入时使用配置边界。",
	"Exposes an input of the Flow Graph Node into the Graph": "将 Flow Graph Node 的输入暴露到图中。",
	"Returns points in A that overlap points in B (Intersection alias).": "返回 A 中与 B 中点重叠的点（交集别名）。",
	"UE naming alias for loading Alembic/imported scene resources as mesh points.": "用于将 Alembic/导入场景资源加载为网格点的 UE 命名别名。",
	"Loads CSV/TSV-style rows as attribute-set data with typed columns.": "将 CSV/TSV 风格的行加载为带类型列的属性集数据。",
	"Loads JSON or Resource-backed PCG point/attribute data into FlowData streams.": "将 JSON 或 Resource 支持的 PCG 点/属性数据加载到 FlowData 流中。",
	"Loops over each element in Stream and runs a graph for each": "遍历流中的每个元素，并为每个元素运行一次图。",
	"Generates a single bounding point at center with size.": "在中心位置生成一个带尺寸的单个边界点。",
	"Creates a single Vector value from 3 inmediate float values": "由 3 个即时浮点值创建一个 Vector 值。",
	"Copies attributes into input data set based on a match_attr.\nThe match_attr is used to pick an asset where the match attribute is the sample in the In and Attributes stream.\nThe weight_attr controls if some assets should be picked more frequently than others.\nIf none are set, a random point from the Attributes entry is picked and assigned to each In point": "根据 match_attr 将属性复制到输入数据集中。\nmatch_attr 用于在 In 与 Attributes 流中按匹配属性选择资源。\nweight_attr 控制某些资源是否应更频繁地被选中。\n如果都未设置，则会从 Attributes 条目中随机选择一个点并分配给每个 In 点。",
	"Applies a math operation between two streams, storing the result in a new stream or overriding another.\nYou can read and write substreams like position.X": "在两个流之间应用数学运算，并将结果存入新流或覆盖另一个流。\n可以读写类似 position.X 的子流。",
	"Merges and combines all streams of all input connections in a single output\nIf input A provides streams s1 and s2, and input B streams s1 and s3\nthe output will have streams s1,s2 and s3 and the default values will be used where the input does not define a value.": "将所有输入连接的全部流合并到单个输出中。\n如果输入 A 提供流 s1 和 s2，输入 B 提供流 s1 和 s3，\n输出将包含 s1、s2 和 s3；输入未定义值的位置会使用默认值。",
	"Samples points on a mesh surface. Alias of Sample Mesh.": "在网格表面采样点。Sample Mesh 的别名。",
	"Generates deterministic per-point seed values from existing seeds, index, and optional position.": "根据已有种子、索引和可选位置，为每个点生成确定性的种子值。",
	"Samples Godot NavigationRegion3D meshes into points.": "将 Godot NavigationRegion3D 网格采样为点。",
	"Outputs an attribute with Noise values": "输出包含噪声值的属性。",
	"Exposes an output parameter of the Subgraph": "暴露子图的一个输出参数。",
	"Partition data based on the different values an attribute.": "根据某个属性的不同值对数据进行分区。",
	"Runs shape-overlap checks per point against the 3D physics world (Godot-specific query node).": "针对 3D 物理世界为每个点执行形状重叠检查（Godot 专用查询节点）。",
	"Sweeps a sphere or box from each point through the Godot physics world.": "从每个点出发，在 Godot 物理世界中扫描球体或盒体。",
	"Point-focused alias of Attribute Filter Range (defaults to position.X).": "面向点数据的 Attribute Filter Range 别名（默认使用 position.X）。",
	"Creates one point per mesh node, using mesh bounds for size and node transform for position/rotation.": "为每个网格节点创建一个点，使用网格边界作为尺寸，并使用节点变换作为位置/旋转。",
	"Emits one point from a Godot player/source Node3D. Resolves by explicit path, group, class/name, then optional camera fallback.": "从 Godot 玩家/源 Node3D 发出一个点。按显式路径、组、类/名称解析，最后可回退到相机。",
	"Computes neighborhood-derived values such as average center, average density, and distance to center.": "计算由邻域派生的值，例如平均中心、平均密度和到中心的距离。",
	"Creates child points around each input point using local or world offsets. Useful for sockets, tabletop dressing, seating layouts, and repeated prop clusters.": "使用局部或世界偏移，在每个输入点周围创建子点。适用于插槽、桌面布置、座位布局和重复道具簇。",
	"Converts point data to attribute-set style data, optionally removing point transform streams.": "将点数据转换为属性集风格数据，并可选择移除点变换流。",
	"Generates one point per used GridMap cell (Godot-specific 3D tile extraction).": "为每个已使用的 GridMap 单元生成一个点（Godot 专用 3D 瓦片提取）。",
	"Loads imported scene/mesh resources and emits one point per mesh instance or mesh asset.": "加载导入的场景/网格资源，并为每个网格实例或网格资源发出一个点。",
	"Generates one point per scene node and optionally imports metadata and selected properties.": "为每个场景节点生成一个点，并可选择导入元数据和指定属性。",
	"Generates one point per used TileMapLayer cell (Godot-specific world extraction).": "为每个已使用的 TileMapLayer 单元生成一个点（Godot 专用世界提取）。",
	"UE naming alias for polygon clipping/filter operations.": "多边形裁剪/过滤操作的 UE 命名别名。",
	"Prints a message that outputs a prefixed message optionally to the log.": "打印一条消息，可选择将带前缀的消息输出到日志。",
	"Generates random colors for each point.": "为每个点生成随机颜色。",
	"Traces a ray in the current scene from the point position (the attribute can be redefined).\nThe output position, rotation and hit result can be stored\nUse a Filter by hit  with True or 1 to remove the points where the trace failed.": "从点位置在当前场景中发射射线（可重新定义该属性）。\n可以存储输出位置、旋转和命中结果。\n使用按 hit 过滤并设为 True 或 1，可移除射线检测失败的点。",
	"Computes the min/max/avg values of the specified stream\nLimited to streams of type float, vector3 or ints.": "计算指定流的最小值、最大值和平均值。\n仅限 float、vector3 或 int 类型的流。",
	"Relax distance between points": "松弛点之间的距离。",
	"Remaps the input values using a curve": "使用曲线重映射输入值。",
	"Remove streams from the input connection.": "从输入连接中移除流。",
	"Replaces all FlowData tags with the provided set.": "用提供的标签集合替换全部 FlowData 标签。",
	"Reroute point — passes data through unchanged": "重路由点：原样传递数据。",
	"Subdivides each int point into a subgrid of regular points with the specified sampling distance": "按指定采样距离，将每个输入点细分为规则点子网格。",
	"Validates that the input data point(s) have a value in the given range.": "验证输入数据点是否拥有给定范围内的值。",
	"Generate points from existing non-flowgraph nodes in the scene\nCan filter by class name, group.\nMetadata values can optionally be imported\nYou can also import properties of the nodes, even with a\nsubpath property like mesh:text if the nodes are a MeshInstance3D with meshes of type TextMesh.": "从场景中现有的非 FlowGraph 节点生成点。\n可按类名、组进行过滤。\n可以选择导入元数据值。\n也可以导入节点属性；如果节点是 MeshInstance3D 且网格为 TextMesh，甚至可以使用 mesh:text 这样的子路径属性。",
	"Selects one of two inputs to be forwarded to a single output based on a Boolean attribute or value.": "根据布尔属性或值，在两个输入中选择一个转发到单个输出。",
	"Selects one of multiple inputs to be forwarded to a single output based on an index attribute or value.": "根据索引属性或值，在多个输入中选择一个转发到单个输出。",
	"Filter inputs by the ratio.\nSo when ratio = 0.2, only 20% of the input points will appear in the output (picked randomly).\nYou can set an attribute name to control which points have more probability to be selected than others.": "按比例过滤输入。\n例如 ratio = 0.2 时，只有 20% 的输入点会随机出现在输出中。\n可以设置属性名来控制哪些点更有概率被选中。",
	"Rejects points that overlap previous points, or removes duplicate grid-cell points.": "拒绝与前序点重叠的点，或移除重复的网格单元点。",
	"Samples 'count' input values from the input, starting at Start and using a 'Step' as gap.\nIf count = 0 means all points.\nNegative values mean backwards": "从输入中采样 count 个值，从 Start 开始，并以 Step 作为间隔。\ncount = 0 表示全部点。\n负值表示反向采样。",
	"Returns the current size of the input sequence": "返回输入序列的当前大小。",
	"Snaps point positions, rotations, or scale sizes to grid values.": "将点的位置、旋转或缩放尺寸吸附到网格值。",
	"Reorders the points based on the values of stream": "根据流的值重新排序点。",
	"Spawns a Mesh Instance on each point, applying the translation, rotation and scale.\nThe instanced mesh can be specified by point if a stream contains the mesh resource to be spawned.\nThe generates meshes are MultiMeshInstance3D.": "在每个点上生成一个 Mesh Instance，并应用平移、旋转和缩放。\n如果某个流包含要生成的网格资源，可按点指定实例网格。\n生成的网格为 MultiMeshInstance3D。",
	"Dynamically instantiates a raw Godot class or custom script node on each point.\nProperties can be transferred from point attributes to node properties.": "在每个点上动态实例化原生 Godot 类或自定义脚本节点。\n可将点属性传递到节点属性。",
	"Similar to spawn meshes but a full scene is instantiated on each node.\nA set of properties can be transfered from the nodes to each instanced scene.": "类似生成网格，但会在每个节点上实例化完整场景。\n可以将一组属性从节点传递到每个实例化场景。",
	"Converts Path3D splines into segment-center points with start/end metadata.": "将 Path3D 样条转换为带起点/终点元数据的线段中心点。",
	"Evaluates a nested graph inside this node": "在该节点内部计算一个嵌套图。",
	"Applies the boolean logic 'substract', where the points of A that overlap points in B are removed.\nThe same node can be changed to return only the points A intersecting the points of B": "应用“减去”布尔逻辑：移除 A 中与 B 中点重叠的点。\n同一节点也可以改为只返回 A 与 B 相交的点。",
	"Samples points randomly inside the bounds of the input points.": "在输入点的边界内随机采样点。",
	"Routes the input to one of multiple outputs based on an index attribute or value.": "根据索引属性或值，将输入路由到多个输出之一。",
	"Adds, removes, or replaces FlowData tags.": "添加、移除或替换 FlowData 标签。",
	"Samples a texture using UV or position-derived coordinates and writes sampled attributes.": "使用 UV 或由位置派生的坐标采样纹理，并写入采样属性。",
	"Applies the random translation/rotation/scale to each point": "对每个点应用随机平移、旋转和缩放。",
	"Godot-facing alias of Transform for point data.": "面向 Godot 点数据的 Transform 别名。",
	"Union alias. Merges all incoming point sets.": "Union 别名。合并所有输入点集。",
	"Samples points inside incoming point volumes (Volume Sampler alias).": "在输入点体积内部采样点（Volume Sampler 别名）。",
	"Stores the input data in a named graph variable and passes it through unchanged.": "将输入数据存入命名图变量，并原样传递。",
